org.smooks.engine.resource.reader

Class NullSourceXMLReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smooks.engine.resource.reader.NullSourceXMLReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContentHandler, SmooksXMLReader, XMLReader

    public class NullSourceXMLReader
extends Object
implements SmooksXMLReader
    Null Source reader.

    Used for null sources. Fires just a single root element ("#document" element) event that can be targeted through the "#document" selector.

    Author:
    tom.fennelly@gmail.com
